ZH: 记得给我买菜。
EN: Remember to buy vegetables for me.

ZH: 记住别忘了明天的约会。
EN: Remember not to forget about tomorrow's appointment.

ZH: 今晚的晚会我一定会记得参加。
EN: I will definitely remember to attend tonight's party.

ZH: 记得把门锁好。
EN: Remember to lock the door.

ZH: 记得查看你的邮箱。
EN: Remember to check your email.

ZH: 记得跟我说话。
EN: Remember to talk to me.

ZH: 记得帮忙打扫房间。
EN: Remember to help clean the room.

ZH: 记得带伞，今天会下雨。
EN: Remember to bring an umbrella, it will rain today.

ZH: 记得给我带些水果。
EN: Remember to bring me some fruits.

ZH: 记得送礼物给妈妈。
EN: Remember to give a present to mom.

ZH: 记下这个地址，我们要去那里。
EN: Remember this address, we need to go there.

ZH: 记得把文件放在桌子上。
EN: Remember to put the documents on the table.

ZH: 记得跟你的朋友打电话。
EN: Remember to call your friend.

ZH: 记住我的电话号码。
EN: Remember my phone number.

ZH: 记得在考试前复习。
EN: Remember to review before the exam.

ZH: 记得帮助那位老人。
EN: Remember to help that old man.

ZH: 记得开心每一天。
EN: Remember to be happy every day.

ZH: 记得给猫食物。
EN: Remember to give food to the cat.

ZH: 记得定好闹铃。
EN: Remember to set the alarm clock.

ZH: 记得把钱包放在包里。
EN: Remember to put your wallet in the bag.
